      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OVERRIDING (1) settled back off the inside but went through his gears strongly to find the frame with a 8 length second (17.98) at this track in Grade 5. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. One of the contenders. CALLA NAUGHTY (7) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish a neck away in second (17.53) at this track in a NG over 300m. Overdue and expected to feature again. SHE'S SILKY (2) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close third, 2 lengths from the winner Frank Chana (18.09) at this track. Expected to feature again. CYCLONE SEBAS (3) deserves plenty of thought over this distance.",
